title.rendered: BOSS AIR SINGLE 220PSI DIGITAL AIR PRESSURE GAUGE

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR SINGLE 220PSI DIGITAL AIR PRESSURE GAUGE

Boss Air Single 220PSI Digital Air Pressure Gauge available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Includes:

  • 1x 220psi Single Digital Gauge 52mm
  • 1 x sender unit
  • 1 x wiring loom
  • 1 x mounting brackets
  • Full instructions

Specs:

  • 0-220psi
  • 1psi increments
  • Red LED = 0-110psi
  • Yellow LED = 111-165psi
  • Green LED =166-220psi
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
